        <hl1>Jones Ruling Meets Letter of Harassment Law; No More Distractions</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Kevin J Williams letter on Apr 2 article on dismissal of Paula Jones's sexual harassment suit against Pres Clinton; drawing (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Now that the Paula Jones case has been thrown out of court (front page, April 2), the two political parties will no longer be distracted from the main business of government, namely selling influence to wealthy campaign contributors.</p>
        <p>KEVIN  J. WILLIAMS  Wynnewood, Pa., April 2, 1998</p>
      </block>
